    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚将开始审查养老基金的非上市资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/australia-to-start-review-of-pension-funds-unlisted-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚养老金监管机构将在未来几个月启动对资产估值和流动性管理实践的审查，因为这个 3.6 万亿澳元（2.4 万亿美元）行业的基金增加了非上市资产的持有量，并面临对这些证券估值的及时性的审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/australia-to-start-review-of-pension-funds-unlisted-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 23:05:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲美元债券销售创 2016 年以来最差开局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/dollar-bond-sales-in-asia-see-worst-start-to-year-since-2016</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着地区借款人在国内筹集更便宜的资金并等待美联储降息，亚洲的美元债券销售迎来了八年来最疲软的开局，与强劲的全球趋势相反。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/dollar-bond-sales-in-asia-see-worst-start-to-year-since-2016</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
